data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-story home nestled on over 1 acre of land. A rare find w/ level, usable land. The wrap-around porch creates a warm & welcoming entrance, setting the stage for the character & grace found within this home. This home boasts a spacious & airy living area that provides the perfect gathering space for entertaining.  The kitchen features SS appliances, a pantry, & an ample storage area. Upstairs, you'll find three spacious bedrooms, including a primary suite w/ a private bathroom & walk-in closet. New roof and fence in 2018. Enjoy the serenity of country living while being just minutes away from all the conveniences of I5, restaurants, shopping, and only 1 hour from the beach.
